or of English, Acadia University, Nova Scotia, Canada.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aSonnets, English. 4aEnglish & American Literature. 4aModern Literature. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / American / General.2bisacsh1 aLewis, Roger C, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aLewis, Roger C, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBoydell and Brewer Complete eBook-Package pre 2013z978311143139040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781846155574?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781846155574423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781846155574/original  a978-3-11-143139-0  Boydell and Brewer Complete eBook-Package pre 2013b2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles